source.name: A&I - NAFTA Safety Stats - NAFTA Safety Stats
source.description: NAFTA Safety Stats presents information and statistics on the U.S. operations of all U.S. registered interstate and intrastate motor carriers broken out by national domicile of the carrier. The information and statistics are presented based on the carrier's domicile within each of the three North American Free Trade Agreement (NAFTA) nations: the United States, Canada, and Mexico. The reports present motor carrier safety statistics for 2005-2009.
